>> name: Sushi Rice
>> author: Guillaume Siegler
>> tags: note-by-note 
>> dsf: S/G

Add some @water{200%grams} into a #bowl{}

Mix in @agar-agar{12%grams}, @glucose{3%grams}, @MSG{2%grams}, @xanthan gum{2%grams}, @corn starch{5%grams} and @acetic acid{10%mL/100mL}

To taste, add @flavouring{2%drops} and @tartaric acid{3%drops}

Mix all the ingredients together, boil in a #pot{} then fill into a #siphon{} and form into a trail
